## Naming Considerations

Catppuccin uses evocative names (rosewater, flamingo, mauve) which work well across diverse applications. Other approaches include:

- Descriptive (blue-500, surface-light)
- Functional (accent-primary, text-body)
- Hybrid (sapphire-accent, crust-background)

Choose naming scheme that:
- Works across all target applications
- Is memorable and consistent
- Doesn't conflict with existing color terminology in target apps